<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.5.6">
<l>kanta māmala reṭṭumiṭṭu niṉkāmar cēvaṭi kaitoḻu teḻum puntiyēṉ maṉattē pukuntāyaip pōkaloṭṭēṉ</l>
<l>canti vēḷvi caṭaṅku nāṉmaṟai yōti yōtuvit tāti yāyvarum</l>
<l>antaṇā ḷaraṟā vaṇiyāli yammāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I will not consent to the departure of you who entered the heart of me</l>
<l rend="indent">whose mind wakes, with palms [joined], adoring your beautiful, rosy feet,</l>
<l>Offering large, fragrant flowers of eight [kinds],</l>
<l>Lord of lovely Āli where priests, who have come [here] from the beginning,</l>
<l rend="indent">	teaching and chanting the four Vedas,</l>
<l>Never cease worship, sacrifices, and rituals.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
